===Proper noun===
'''[[Latvian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Latvian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Latvia|Republic of Latvia]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1940-1941 and 1944-1991).

